{"tid":2246771,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國安顧問重申駐阿富汗美軍明年初減至2500人","createTime":"2020-10-17T10:35:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-17T10:35:45.000Z","uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"ce7da9c8c796ae599fa989cad0f820d047517459","tid":2246771,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T10:35:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1555264-20201017.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1555264-20201017.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=6FpmejEDNbHOA1ae24hao1SbKypX9O9wpAPGBeI%2BXHg%3D&h=107605ff\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1555264-20201017.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=0e081435\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1555264-20201017.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n美國國家安全顧問奧布萊恩重申，駐阿富汗美軍明年年初將減少至約2500人。<br />\n<br />\n奧布萊恩出席一個網上安全論壇時強調，這計劃不是「推測」，而是總統命令，並稱五角大樓正在執行該計劃。<br />\n<br />\n總統特朗普日前在社交網站提出，駐阿美軍應於今年聖誕節前回國。奧布萊恩說，特朗普這表態是其本人的「願望」。"}]}